item.title: Freaky
item.dc:creator: boutje777
item.description: This page is a sort of a remembrance for the best petfriend i ever had, Freaky the budgie. Someone made this portrait for me She died september 2020 and i buried her behind my house so she was still around a little and i could keep an eye at her and visit and bring flowers […]
item.content:encoded:
This page is a sort of a remembrance for the best petfriend i ever had, Freaky the budgie.

Someone made this portrait for me

She died september 2020 and i buried her behind my house so she was still around a little and i could keep an eye at her and visit and bring flowers whenever i felt to.
Last week i noticed some people with heavy machinery were working nearby and i asked what they were doing, i understand that they would remove all bushes and trees all around, also at the place where i buried Freaky. So i hurried and dug her up, luckily the casket was still in good shape, i took her with me inside and made the decision that i would make a place for her at my balcony so i knew for 100% she would be in a good place. I just feel that i have to take care of her even after her dead, and this makes me feel alot better knowing she will be in peace at my balcony.

This is now her place.

For the 1st time on my hand.

Always on my keyboard when i needed it

On the monitor when i was working on compilations.

Hey, are you paying attention

With her boyfriend Zowie

Here some short movies

She is listening to Joy Division

https://youtu.be/o_–rYJmml4&w=400&h=320

She always came to me whenever i raise my arm

https://youtu.be/oSjkH_4AgCM&w=400&h=320
